{
  "stem": "7273.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And thanks to the Poles, when we were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] settle-- resettled-- not resettled, but taken away, they actually told the Germans where we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a hiding place, but they sort of said, there are Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we had to come out and so on, my mother wanted to bribe this German fellow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, look, I gladly would.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the Poles said it to my commander, so I can't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By-- yes, by the Poles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- we-- we had a room and a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was all we had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked in a factory where military coats were sewn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mom was secretary to a very high German Nazi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because she was very good in stenography and typing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the German language, as such, so that she had this position.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were the last transport, because they took us away in transports.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were the last.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was the 18th February, '43.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'41 and '42, and the beginning of '43, we were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, conditions, food-wise, which is the most important part, was not very easy to survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mom had special ability to earn still a little bit, and through our German house [GERMAN]--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was a-- it was a-- like here, a manager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A manager for properties.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- he was our manager for-- my parents' manager for 20 years, because our-- some of our properties were in Breslau.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- Katowice was Poland, and Breslau was Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had this fellow who looked after everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was his name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gustaf Wagner.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came twice yearly to us and brought us whatever he collected and discussed things.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
